Thank you for choosing PrestoStay, the student hostel payment portal. At PrestoStay, we are dedicated to safeguarding your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data.

1. Information We Collect:

a. Personal Information:

Full name
Contact information (email address, phone number)
Student identification details
Billing and payment details
b. Transaction Information:

Details of payments made through the portal
c. Device and Usage Information:

IP address
Browser type
Usage patterns on our portal
2. How We Use Your Information:

a. Processing Payments:

To facilitate and process student hostel booking payments
b. Communication:

To communicate with you regarding your booking, payments, and other relevant information
c. User Experience Improvement:

To analyze and enhance the functionality and user experience of the PrestoStay payment portal
d. Legal Compliance:

To comply with legal obligations and regulations
3. Information Sharing:

a. Service Providers:

We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in processing payments and providing related services.
b. Legal Requirements:

We may disclose your information when required by law or in response to legal processes.
4. Security Measures:

a. We implement advanced security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

b. Payment information is processed securely using industry-standard encryption technologies.

5. Retention of Personal Information:

We will retain your personal information for the duration necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.

6. Your Choices:

a. You have the right to update or correct your personal information at any time.

b. You may opt out of receiving promotional communications from PrestoStay.

7. Changes to the Privacy Policy:

We reserve the right to update and make changes to this Privacy Policy. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated policy on the PrestoStay website.

8. Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact PrestoStay at [contact email/phone number].

By using PrestoStay, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
